author: danielsh
msg: This record-only-merges r1145519 from trunk, which removed the option there
prior to the 1.7.0 release.  (See also r1145515.)
The test harness has to allow SERVER_MINOR_VERSION=7, as that is used for the
server_has_atomic_revprop() helper.  It may or may not accept
SERVER_MINOR_VERSION=8 at this time, but if it doesn't then that should be
fixed (eventually) on trunk, rather than on this branch.
